Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:02.44,Base,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.76,0:00:05.32,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:09.80,Base,,0,0,0,,Check it out! This is the Kouka uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:12.59,Base,,0,0,0,,I know. I have one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:15.76,Base,,0,0,0,,Guidance Week and the entrance ceremony\Nare finally behind us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:18.21,Base,,0,0,0,,and tomorrow, we get to start classes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:21.67,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was so excited last night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:29.92,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll at least {\i0}try {\i1}to\Nwake her up this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.07,0:00:32.17,Base,,0,0,0,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:35.39,Base,,0,0,0,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:47.33,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, she's not waking up. I tried.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:49.34,Base,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Narata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:51.71,Base,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sugimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:54.51,Base,,0,0,0,,Where is our troublesome Watanabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:55.91,Base,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:00:58.79,Base,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'll be entering your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:01.97,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe! Watanabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:03.84,Base,,0,0,0,,Come on, Watanabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:07.77,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe Sarasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:11.76,Base,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:14.43,Base,,0,0,0,,You can {\i1}not {\i0}be late\Non your very first day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:17.24,Base,,0,0,0,,Get ready at once and come \Nto the auditorium!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:18.53,Base,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:21.48,Base,,0,0,0,,Wait, it's only 5:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:24.48,Base,,0,0,0,,Do we have\Nexercises with the JSDF again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:28.52,Base,,0,0,0,,No. We're meeting people who are\N{\i1}much {\i0}scarier than the JSDF.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:50.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Everyone dreams of becoming a superstar at least once
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:55.77,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So that you can make the world envious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.77,0:01:58.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}1, 2, 3, quick like Allegro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:00.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Hold that hand and come
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:05.34,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Let's build a rainbow together at Andante
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:11.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}You aren't anyone right now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:16.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So any of your future can come true
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:22.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Your dream is just beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:27.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Little by little, you can become yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:33.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Tomorrow's gonna blow another wind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:37.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So dream as many times as you want
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:42.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Someday, become the stage's sparkling star
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:47.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}so that the spotlight shines upon you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:03.55,Base,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1520,999)}"Those Who Long to\NCross the Silver Bridge"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:04.85,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,Good morning! I am the first-year\Nstudent representative, Sugimoto Sawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:06.67,Base,,0,0,0,,We're very sorry we're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:11.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you're not late.\NThere's still five minutes till 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:13.13,Base,,0,0,0,,Our centennial class is so diligent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:15.22,Base,,0,0,0,,Who are these lovely ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:19.76,Base,,0,0,0,,Those are the second-year students,\Nthe 99th Kouka Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:20.76,Base,,0,0,0,,Keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:23.63,Base,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto Sawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:28.40,Base,,0,0,0,,I see you are representing your class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.04,Base,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:36.13,Base,,0,0,0,,The faculty told me the highest\Nexam scorer earns that privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.66,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:41.30,Base,,0,0,0,,Good morning, first-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.30,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm the second-year representative,\NTakei Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.68,Base,,0,0,0,,Today, in accordance\Nwith school tradition,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:50.85,Base,,0,0,0,,we will show you the ropes\N for morning cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:52.98,Base,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:54.90,Base,,0,0,0,,--Thank you!\N--Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.17,Base,,0,0,0,,--Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.77,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll be a top star!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.78,Base,,0,0,0,,It's our pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:11.54,Base,,0,0,0,,Each first-year has been assigned\Na second-year student advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:17.59,Base,,0,0,0,,They will support you and give you advice\Nthroughout your next year here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:20.66,Base,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, who's my advisor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.22,Base,,0,0,0,,There she goes, how annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:27.16,Base,,0,0,0,,Depending upon your advisor,\Nyour life here can be a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.25,Base,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, Risa, you're scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:32.98,Base,,0,0,0,,Now, when your names are called,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:36.51,Base,,0,0,0,,please go to the cleaning location with your advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:39.86,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Japanese Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.51,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll be your advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.64,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm Nojima Hijiri, vice-president of\Nthe second-year class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.20,Base,,0,0,0,,It's so good to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:45.63,Base,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:50.91,Base,,0,0,0,,Your eyelashes are so long,\Nand your skin is so fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:53.21,Base,,0,0,0,,No wonder you got to be in JPX!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:53.98,Base,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.84,Base,,0,0,0,,Everyone was fighting over\Nwho got to be your advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:00.90,Base,,0,0,0,,We did rock-paper-scissors\N for it, and I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:04.91,Base,,0,0,0,,I felt like I'd been chosen\Nto be the center for JPX!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:06.76,Base,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:11.31,Base,,0,0,0,,Are you not a morning person?\NOr have you low blood pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:11.93,Base,,0,0,0,,Neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:15.98,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm a {\i1}huge {\i0}JPX fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:19.09,Base,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't gotten into Kouka,\NI might've auditioned for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:26.01,Base,,0,0,0,,I mean, everyone in JPX is so cute and\Nlively, with their big, sparkling smiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:30.81,Base,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm so honored\Nto be your advisor for the next...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:33.31,Base,,0,0,0,,You weren't one of my fans, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.33,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:44.34,Base,,0,0,0,,You start sweeping from\N one side of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.05,Base,,0,0,0,,And don't whack it on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:48.51,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay. I've never cleaned a room before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.30,Base,,0,0,0,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:54.67,Base,,0,0,0,,So why do you think\NI wasn't one of your fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:59.48,Base,,0,0,0,,Because I'm not lively and\NI don't have a big, sparkling smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:03.43,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing you're a fan\Nof Kozono Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.24,Base,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I liked you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:10.57,Base,,0,0,0,,Your whole 'not smiling' thing\Nmade you this cool-headed beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.72,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.89,Base,,0,0,0,,So you probably wish to play\N Female Lead, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.67,Base,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:20.90,Base,,0,0,0,,You mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.24,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't have any specific wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:26.12,Base,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:31.26,Base,,0,0,0,,Well, I think you'll be glad \Nyou got me as your advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:35.50,Base,,0,0,0,,Some second-years are going to be\Nreally mean to their first-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:40.02,Base,,0,0,0,,The competition starts\Nlong before you get into the Troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:43.32,Base,,0,0,0,,It started the moment\Nyou got into this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:46.86,Base,,0,0,0,,But I don't think you'll have to\Nworry about it, Narata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:48.85,Base,,0,0,0,,C'mon, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.81,Base,,0,0,0,,This is how you use a broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:55.49,Base,,0,0,0,,Keep your hands apart,\Nand place your dominant hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:02.17,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm Nakayama Risa,\Nand I'll be your student advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:06.17,Base,,0,0,0,,Yay, my advisor's a Latin beauty\Nwith a rockin' bod!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.12,Base,,0,0,0,,And I hate when people point that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:12.22,Base,,0,0,0,,You'll be cleaning this traditional dance classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.11,Base,,0,0,0,,for next two hours before class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.58,Base,,0,0,0,,First, sweep the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:20.33,Base,,0,0,0,,After that, prick the dirt off the floor using pin\Nand wipe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.67,Base,,0,0,0,,Brush off the dust from the window frames.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:26.44,Base,,0,0,0,,And don't leave a single stain on the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.49,Base,,0,0,0,,I have two hours to do\Nthat all by myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:29.32,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.30,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.04,Base,,0,0,0,,This is taking forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:40.82,Base,,0,0,0,,It better not, or you'll be late to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.98,Base,,0,0,0,,That'd be a {\i1}big {\i0}problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.84,Base,,0,0,0,,How tall are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.00,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm 178 centimeters tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:50.32,Base,,0,0,0,,And your age?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:51.99,Base,,0,0,0,,Fifteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:58.10,Base,,0,0,0,,I got in when I was in 12th grade,\Nso I'm 19. I'll be 20 next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:59.21,Base,,0,0,0,,It sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:03.23,Base,,0,0,0,,Why? You're brimming with\Nmature ladylike energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.67,Base,,0,0,0,,Cut the chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.04,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:09.68,Base,,0,0,0,,It's just that I really like\Ntalking with you, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.93,Base,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:14.32,Base,,0,0,0,,Then I'll find something\Nyou'll like talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:15.56,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:20.34,Base,,0,0,0,,Figured! I'd better focus on this\Ncleaning, or it really {\i1}will {\i0}take forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:24.50,Base,,0,0,0,,You wanna be Oscar, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:28.25,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes! I came to this school so I could\Nlearn how to play Lady Os-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.40,Base,,0,0,0,,Well, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:30.48,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:35.25,Base,,0,0,0,,You'll never play Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:45.69,Base,,0,0,0,,It will never happen! Not ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:50.98,Base,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how good you are,\Nor how much natural talent you possess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:54.59,Base,,0,0,0,,No way in the world will you {\i1}ever{\i0}\Nbe able to play Sukeroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:08:59.10,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.88,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.15,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, Watanabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:11.36,Base,,0,0,0,,Why? Why can't I be Lady Oscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.59,Base,,0,0,0,,Look, stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.62,Base,,0,0,0,,They're gonna think I'm bullying you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:21.87,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's too tall to play Lady Oscar, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:25.69,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The actress playing André\Nwould have to be taller than her,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:26.88,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,Why can't I play her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:26.88,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and it's impossible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:31.89,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also, none of us wanted\Nto be your advisor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:35.64,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sticking out like a sore thumb\Nis fatal in this women world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:40.16,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I told her that, though,\Nhow badly would she react?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:46.52,Base,,0,0,0,,Wow, so you want to be\Na top Female Lead, too, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:52.13,Base,,0,0,0,,Shh! Don't tell anyone yet, Hijiri!\NI'm still kinda shy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:54.09,Base,,0,0,0,,They're gonna say\Nit doesn't fit my personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.66,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:10:00.83,Base,,0,0,0,,You're gorgeous, Risa, and you're one of\Nthe best singers and dancers we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.79,Base,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:07.04,Base,,0,0,0,,But your voice and look might not fit a Female Lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:11.61,Base,,0,0,0,,Y'know, you'd be way better off\Nplaying older women as a Woman Lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:12.44,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.25,Base,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're so sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:17.41,Base,,0,0,0,,But you're not exactly sweet nor\N tidy-looking, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:21.45,Base,,0,0,0,,You'd be perfect playing Jeanne,\Nor Carlotta, or Kurotokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:24.31,Base,,0,0,0,,Evil villainess roles would be {\i1}perfect {\i0}for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.96,Base,,0,0,0,,Man, though, if you were\Njust a little taller,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.82,Base,,0,0,0,,being a top Male Lead\Nwouldn't be just a dream for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:34.09,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the day I learned\Nthat only girls like Hijiri{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:36.51,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}had a chance of becoming\Na top Female Lead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:40.48,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls with angelic faces, strong\Ndetermination, and a mean streak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:45.35,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,Why can't I play Lady Oscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:45.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:51.05,Base,,0,0,0,,I know! You stood under the cherry tree\Nbefore the welcome ceremony, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.05,Base,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:56.43,Base,,0,0,0,,"Noone who stood the Kouka\Ncherry tree before admission,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:11:01.66,Base,,0,0,0,,"has never become a \NKouka top star in past 100 years."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.01,Base,,0,0,0,,That's the tree's curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:05.99,Base,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:06.79,Base,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:11.54,Base,,0,0,0,,Then I'm gonna break that curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:15.45,Base,,0,0,0,,I couldn't be here if I was a guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.47,Base,,0,0,0,,but I was lucky enough to be born a girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:20.91,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and {\i0}I got picked to study here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:26.92,Base,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as absolutes\Nwhen it comes to {\i1}can {\i0}or {\i1}can't{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:32.84,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let such \Nmeaningless curse hold me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:36.78,Base,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.06,Base,,0,0,0,,'Cause nobody knows\Nwhat you're capable of?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:41.64,Base,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:43.60,Base,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:45.21,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:48.48,Base,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:49.73,Base,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:53.63,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a special assistance today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:57.01,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How nice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:00.38,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"First-Year Lockers"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:00.24,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:03.76,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe! I was starting to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:05.76,Base,,0,0,0,,Here I thought you'd messed up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:06.87,Base,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:10.68,Base,,0,0,0,,If one of us first-years messes up,\Nwe all get punished for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:13.94,Base,,0,0,0,,The second-years will yell at {\i1}all {\i0}of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:17.88,Base,,0,0,0,,Your advisor seemed kinda strict,\Nso hopefully that means you did okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:23.20,Base,,0,0,0,,Yep! Risa doesn't mince words,\Nbut she's really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.89,Base,,0,0,0,,She {\i1}definitely {\i0}messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:28.08,Base,,0,0,0,,Our advisors were\Nscary, too, right, Chika?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:31.98,Base,,0,0,0,,She stared daggers at me when I\Ndropped the broom earlier, Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.75,Base,,0,0,0,,Kouka activites are really intense, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:39.18,Base,,0,0,0,,But your advisor looked\Nreally nice, Narata!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.35,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:46.14,Base,,0,0,0,,How was our Lady Oscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:49.06,Base,,0,0,0,,Nothing special. She's still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:53.81,Base,,0,0,0,,My, what's wrong, Risa? You look happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:56.06,Base,,0,0,0,,You must have it rough, Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:59.65,Base,,0,0,0,,People think Naracchi could be\Na top Female Lead one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.84,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what you're implying,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.82,Base,,0,0,0,,but you're definitely mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:08.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Naracchi has zero motivation \Nfor Kouka, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:14.57,Base,,0,0,0,,Well, you never know what wind\Nwill lift her sails in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:26.18,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Sarasa: First class is ballet.\NWearing a leotard makes me feel so girly.\NEveryone is so good at ballet, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:26.18,Base,,0,0,0,,"Jiraiya: Kabuki practice all day today."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:31.00,Base,,0,0,0,,What do you want, Kouzaburou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:33.71,Base,,0,0,0,,Those are Sarasa's tweets,\Nright? Lemme see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:39.06,Base,,0,0,0,,I need to make sure you and Sarasa\Nare keeping it wholesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.65,Base,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:45.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Remind me, Akiya,\Nwho bought that tablet for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:53.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Ooh, a cool Latin senior advisor taught her\Nhow to clean a classroom today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.86,Base,,0,0,0,,Even I haven't read that far yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:58.74,Base,,0,0,0,,Wipe that look off your face, Akiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:02.69,Base,,0,0,0,,Your biggest fans are older women.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:05.07,Base,,0,0,0,,No rude looks, or you'll lose them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:10.62,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Sarasa: A cool Latin beauty\Ntaught me how to clean a classroom."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:10.62,Base,,0,0,0,,Sarasa-san's 15, too?\NShe must be getting big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:14.60,Base,,0,0,0,,She is. She's already taller than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.63,Base,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:20.98,Base,,0,0,0,,She was so tiny when she was\Ntaking dance lessons with you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.01,Base,,0,0,0,,I wish we could've kept her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:25.70,Base,,0,0,0,,But she's in Kobe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:28.64,Base,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll go sneak a peek at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:31.10,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't be a creepy stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:32.83,Base,,0,0,0,,By the way, Akiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:33.66,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:36.96,Base,,0,0,0,,Coming to you is getting annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:40.44,Base,,0,0,0,,Could you give me the password\Nfor this account?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.63,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm Andou, your acting teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:53.14,Base,,0,0,0,,So I'd planned on talking about\NShakespearean dramas today,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:54.25,Base,,0,0,0,,but change of plans:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:57.54,Base,,0,0,0,,Today, we'll introduce\Nourselves to the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.00,Base,,0,0,0,,Mr. Andou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:04.76,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't think we should waste our\N important class time on self-introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:07.97,Base,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll start with the introductions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:09.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Hold on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:13.73,Base,,0,0,0,,You all know\Nthis is no normal school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.00,Base,,0,0,0,,When you graduate from a high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:21.36,Base,,0,0,0,,you'd normally go on to college, find a job,\N take an apprenticeship, get married, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.70,Base,,0,0,0,,But here, you've got but two options:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:28.37,Base,,0,0,0,,Sink or swim. Continue or drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.72,Base,,0,0,0,,When you graduate,\Nyou'll join the Kouka Troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:36.08,Base,,0,0,0,,That means you're stuck together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:39.64,Base,,0,0,0,,It'd be a good idea for you\Nto learn more about one another
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:44.46,Base,,0,0,0,,so that you can make your\N life together here easier even just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:46.48,Base,,0,0,0,,Very well, Mr. Andou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:49.47,Base,,0,0,0,,Then, as our class representative, I will go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:51.22,Base,,0,0,0,,There goes Miss Bossypants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:53.91,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm Sugimoto Sawa, and I'm 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:59.20,Base,,0,0,0,,My family runs a ballet studio in Tokyo,\Nwhere I studied ballet from a young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.87,Base,,0,0,0,,Though going abroad was in the topic,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:05.25,Base,,0,0,0,,but since I want to\Nperform musical theater,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:08.49,Base,,0,0,0,,so I applied to the Kouka School of\NMusical and Theatrical Arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.45,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm honored to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.80,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm Hoshino Kaoru, and I'm 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:18.93,Base,,0,0,0,,My mom and grandmother were both\N Spring Troupe Female Leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:21.89,Base,,0,0,0,,But because I've got this great height,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.40,Base,,0,0,0,,I intend to play Male Lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:26.15,Base,,0,0,0,,I'd like to add that\NI want to be an Male Lead as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.93,Base,,0,0,0,,All right, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:29.48,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm Sawada Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.51,Base,,0,0,0,,And I'm Sawada Chika!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:35.91,Base,,0,0,0,,Chika got in last year, but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:40.44,Base,,0,0,0,,So I waited a year so we could\Nboth get in together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:43.50,Base,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm Yamada Ayako.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:46.46,Base,,0,0,0,,I've loved Kouka ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.75,Base,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I actually got in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:51.82,Base,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, I'm going to give my all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:54.80,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm Watanabe Sarasa, and I'm 15!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:57.70,Base,,0,0,0,,I've always dreamed of\Nplaying Lady Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.64,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes, we know,\Nyou're going to be a top star, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:04.23,Base,,0,0,0,,Right! I love anime, manga,\Nand period pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:08.69,Base,,0,0,0,,and I live in Asakusa in Tokyo with my\NGrandpa Ken, who makes tatami mats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:11.15,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, and we have a cat named Nono!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Nono's nose is always twitching-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.97,Base,,0,0,0,,Tell us more about your cat later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:16.55,Base,,0,0,0,,All right, last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.14,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm Narata Ai. I'm 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.60,Base,,0,0,0,,I've done ballet since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:27.66,Base,,0,0,0,,I was taught by my uncle, Narata Taichi,\Nwho's a ballet teacher here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.19,Base,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:32.71,Base,,0,0,0,,Really? You know there's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:39.18,Base,,0,0,0,,My mother is an\Nactress, Narata Kimiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:43.48,Base,,0,0,0,,I was in JPX48 and was\N13th in the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:45.14,Base,,0,0,0,,After that, I quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:49.38,Base,,0,0,0,,They {\i1}made {\i0}me quit,\Nso I came here. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:54.81,Base,,0,0,0,,Wow, you were a JPX idol, Ai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:56.15,Base,,0,0,0,,I had no idea-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.28,Base,,0,0,0,,Well, that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:01.45,Base,,0,0,0,,Let's head out for our tour\Nof the Kouka Theatre's backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:02.27,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:03.75,Base,,0,0,0,,Backstage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:08.07,Base,,0,0,0,,I got permission to take you on\Na tour from two to three today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:11.78,Base,,0,0,0,,You'll see that the stage doesn't\Nbelong to just its actresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.30,Base,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:19.12,Base,,0,0,0,,First, we have the costuming department.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:22.91,Base,,0,0,0,,The embellishments are all\Nhand-sewn! Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:26.56,Base,,0,0,0,,I know those gigantic feathers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:30.81,Base,,0,0,0,,Those are worn by the top Male Lead\Nof the Winter Troupe, like Kazahana Sou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.84,Base,,0,0,0,,They're too incredible to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.40,Base,,0,0,0,,My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:38.26,Base,,0,0,0,,The bunny girl costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:43.48,Base,,0,0,0,,Wow! Look at this mountain of dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.98,Base,,0,0,0,,It's just like Rose Bertin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:48.01,Base,,0,0,0,,I feel like Rosalie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.98,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Rose what?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.98,Base,,0,0,0,,Right, Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:51.93,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:53.21,Base,,0,0,0,,What do we say, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:56.45,Base,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:59.09,Base,,0,0,0,,I saw Naracchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:01.53,Base,,0,0,0,,She might try to lie low, but she still stands out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:03.39,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll have to brag to my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:05.64,Base,,0,0,0,,Did you see that other stand-out girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:09.00,Base,,0,0,0,,The one with the twinkling eyes\Nand the towering height.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:14.32,Base,,0,0,0,,The set department is just right behind the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:15.38,Base,,0,0,0,,That's a design.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:17.53,Base,,0,0,0,,That's a long brush!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.35,Base,,0,0,0,,I've never seen one like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:23.33,Base,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's all Styrofoam!\NBut it looks so real!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.85,Base,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.45,Base,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Watanabe, don't get in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.36,Base,,0,0,0,,It's all good, Mr. Andou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:34.13,Base,,0,0,0,,Gettin' praise from future actresses\Ngets us all motivated to work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.96,Base,,0,0,0,,Great! I'm gonna be a top star one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:39.62,Base,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll make \Nan awesome set for me then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.16,Base,,0,0,0,,There she goes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:46.89,Base,,0,0,0,,Well, all right! No goin' back\Non a bold statement like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:49.35,Base,,0,0,0,,We'll be waitin' for ya then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.17,Base,,0,0,0,,Yep! We got ourselves a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:53.46,Base,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:12.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, you idiot! Watanabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.13,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't go through there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:16.63,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:18.14,Base,,0,0,0,,That's the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:46.34,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe! Get back here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:50.19,Base,,0,0,0,,And don't you dare walk out\Non the Silver Bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:51.87,Base,,0,0,0,,The Silver Bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:54.92,Base,,0,0,0,,The Silver Bridge is the most \Nprominent part of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:59.70,Base,,0,0,0,,Only Kouka's most dazzling stars\Ncan cross that bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:07.76,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah, only the top Male Lead and\NFemale Lead and a handful of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:11.62,Base,,0,0,0,,That's what we all aim for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:13.93,Base,,0,0,0,,The Silver Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.98,Base,,0,0,0,,Someone's out on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:23.78,Base,,0,0,0,,Judging from height, it's probably Yama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:25.20,Base,,0,0,0,,Pop a light on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:36.21,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To become one of Kouka's top stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:40.21,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you need hard work,\Ntalent, star quality,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:44.57,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and enough luck to be\Ngiven the right chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:48.08,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watanabe Sarasa's stage presence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.15,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was dazzling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.59,0:21:59.34,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Ex-JPX idol Ai Narata\Nenrolls in Kouka School!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:03.20,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm finally here in Kobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}I'll keep walking on the path
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:29.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}that glows white in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.86,0:22:33.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}A long, narrow path
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:35.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}that can only be walked alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.86,0:22:37.61,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}I walk forward so that 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.61,0:22:42.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}I won't fall behind other people's shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:46.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}If I just head straight forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:49.69,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}it'll appear right in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:53.18,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Now, let's open the door
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.69,0:22:57.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}There are sparkling stars in this vast sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}If just I had wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:03.01,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}I'd flap and flutter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.01,0:23:07.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}high through the space like a bird
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:11.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Going around the constellations,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.00,0:23:13.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}and pursuing the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.38,0:23:20.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}we had just started this endless journey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:39.96,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Act 3: The Teddy Bear"
